#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Crazy Pets!"
msgstr "瘋狂寵物！"

#. ~ Description for Crazy Pets!
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Adds new, crazier pet starts!  WARNING: Breaks intended balance."
msgstr "添加更瘋狂的新寵物開局！警告：會破壞遊戲平衡性。"

#: .\monstermount.json
msgid "chicken walker"
msgid_plural "chicken walkers"
msgstr[0] "雞足步行機"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'chicken walker'}
#: .\monstermount.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop ATSV, a massive, heavily-armed and armored robot walking on a "
"pair of reverse-jointed legs.  Armed with a 40mm anti-vehicle grenade "
"launcher, 5.56 anti-personnel gun, and the ability to electrify itself "
"against attackers, it is an effective automated sentry, though production "
"was limited due to a legal dispute."
msgstr ""
"諾斯羅普 ATSV，一種龐大、重武裝且裝甲厚重的機器人，以一對反關節腿行走。裝備有 40 毫米反車輛榴彈發射器、5.56 "
"毫米反人員機槍，並能對攻擊者釋放電擊，是一種高效的自動哨兵，但因法律糾紛產量有限。"

#: .\monstermount.json
msgid "Beagle Mini-Tank UGV"
msgid_plural "Beagle Mini-Tank UGVs"
msgstr[0] "比格微型坦克無人地面載具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Beagle Mini-Tank UGV'}
#: .\monstermount.json
msgid ""
"The Northrop Beagle is a refrigerator-sized urban warfare UGV.  Sporting an "
"anti-tank missile launcher, 40mm grenade launcher, and numerous anti-"
"infantry weapons, it's designed for high-risk urban fighting."
msgstr "諾斯羅普比格是一種冰箱大小的城市戰無人地面載具。配備反坦克導彈發射器、40 毫米榴彈發射器和多種反步兵武器，專為高風險城市戰鬥設計。"

#: .\monstermount.json
msgid "shoggoth"
msgid_plural "shoggoths"
msgstr[0] "修格斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'shoggoth'}
#: .\monstermount.json
msgid ""
"A gargantuan protoplasmic blob, constantly reshaping, forming new pseudopods"
" seemingly at will.  All over its body are eyes that form and disappear.  It"
" looks at you with malice."
msgstr "一個巨大的原生質團塊，不斷重塑形態，彷彿隨意地形成新的偽足。其全身遍佈著形成又消失的眼睛。它帶著惡意注視著你。"

